  {
    
    "name": "Section 2",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-626145919594660403 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/ywhwyf-mp/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=626145919544328755&sectionId=626145919594660403)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gguCnwVa854_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gguCnwVa854_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Frame_1484580952_80c40562-ca10-49d4-9ebc-102373a42a14.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","label":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","default":"7 Reasons Why 40,000+ Women in 30’s, 40’s &amp; 50’s switched from trendy beauty products to our affordable Anti-Wrinkle Collagen Mask for Smoother &amp; Firmer Skin."},{"type":"html","id":"ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_8.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","label":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","default":"<p>By Nicole Johnson | Updated: August 2025</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDMsYPdOaL_text","label":"ggDMsYPdOaL_text","default":"<p>After years of chasing glow with overpriced serums, I found this collagen mask that actually feels made for women like me. <strong>As someone in my 40s who’s tried countless masks,</strong> I finally get <strong>why over 15,000 women keep coming back to this one</strong> — it works.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHaZg1HJ-u_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggHaZg1HJ-u_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_7.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDsY4j7iCg_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggDsY4j7iCg_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/3_7.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3-ryG7PDx_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg3-ryG7PDx_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/4_7.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ0KO9nzT-_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggZ0KO9nzT-_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/5_6.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_uJ1UkSmj_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg_uJ1UkSmj_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/6_6.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtUZTT-Jz9_text","label":"ggtUZTT-Jz9_text","default":"1. Affordable Skin Transformation"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsWY_OmHqm_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsWY_OmHqm_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Anti-Wrinkle_Main_Photo_1_175ab694-d2b1-4cae-a2bb-0e991b2fdc09.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1I25rv2az_text","label":"gg1I25rv2az_text","default":"<p>Who says fighting wrinkles has to be expensive? <strong>The right products can deliver remarkable results without breaking the bank.</strong> This Anti-Wrinkle Collagen Mask is proof that you don't need luxury prices to get potent, effective ingredients <strong>for visibly smoother and more youthful-looking skin.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPWgmTwPwm_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggPWgmTwPwm_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/For_LP_9.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoUY9dwYA6_text","label":"ggoUY9dwYA6_text","default":"2. Deep Hydration &amp; Smooth Skin in Just One Use"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzF8IwNJdT_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggzF8IwNJdT_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/a42llv_1cd48bf7-ccbb-41e2-b138-c102bae3f781.gif"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzF8IwNJdT_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggzF8IwNJdT_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/a42llv.gif?v=1756138727"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJ3-7_jpjI_text","label":"ggJ3-7_jpjI_text","default":"<p>As we age, <strong>our skin's ability to retain moisture lessons, leading to the appearance of fine lines and a dull complexion.</strong> While regular moisturizers provide surface-level hydration, this mask goes deeper. Its unique gel texture sinks into the skin, delivering intense hydration that plumps up the skin and smooths out wrinkles. <strong>It leaves my skin feeling instantly soothed, hydrated, and glowing for hours.</strong> Even after a long day, my face still looks refreshed and revitalized.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbFbBP2HOr_text","label":"ggbFbBP2HOr_text","default":"3. Scientifically Proven Ingredients (Without Heavy Oils)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzd5H2V5f7_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggzd5H2V5f7_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/10_2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gggwGvdZpTa_text","label":"gggwGvdZpTa_text","default":"<p><strong>What you put on your skin matters.</strong> I was impressed to find that this mask is formulated with hydrolyzed marine collagen, <strong>which is broken down into smaller molecules to better penetrate the skin's surface.</strong> It’s also packed with skin-loving ingredients like <strong>Centella Asiatica to soothe and repair, and glycerin for an extra boost of hydration.</strong> This fragrance-free and gentle formula is designed to deliver visible results without irritation.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8P26fUryi_label","label":"gg8P26fUryi_label","default":"<p>SHOP NOW</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtL_icosgY_text","label":"ggtL_icosgY_text","default":"4. A Low-Effort Glow-Up for Busy Women"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ9E31I1TS_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggQ9E31I1TS_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/4_8.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2e1m2cC1B_text","label":"gg2e1m2cC1B_text","default":"<p>No time? No problem. This anti-wrinkle mask delivers noticeable results in just one step. <strong>There's no need for complicated layering or waiting around.</strong> In under two hours, my skin looks smoother, fresher, and has a healthy glow. <strong>It's my go-to for a quick and effective skin refresh, especially when I'm short on time.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVQu2rVfXF_text","label":"ggVQu2rVfXF_text","default":"5. It’s Safe for Sensitive and Reactive Skin"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNCSuMhJSO_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggNCSuMhJSO_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/12_2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv20YPCwvh_text","label":"ggv20YPCwvh_text","default":"<p>I'm always cautious when recommending masks, <strong>as many contain ingredients that can irritate sensitive skin.</strong> This mask stands out because of its minimal and gentle formula. <strong>It's designed to be well-tolerated by a wide range of skin types, offering a soothing and calming experience even for those with reactive skin.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_EmekCIcb_text","label":"gg_EmekCIcb_text","default":"6. Cooling &amp; Soothing Effect"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOfBmitjRW_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggOfBmitjRW_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/13_2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggELAxbcF6Y_text","label":"ggELAxbcF6Y_text","default":"<p>One of my favorite things about this mask is the <strong>refreshing, cooling sensation it provides.</strong> It’s a simple, luxurious way to unwind and take care of your skin at home. <strong>This spa-like experience soothes, hydrates, and leaves you with a radiant glow.</strong> If you haven't tried it yet, you're in for a treat.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKdy7yOoKn_text","label":"ggKdy7yOoKn_text","default":"7. The Data and the Real People Back It Up"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7mIFh6pXb_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg7mIFh6pXb_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/14_2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA658ziimh_text","label":"ggA658ziimh_text","default":"<p>The proof is in the results. <strong>Clinical reviews and user feedback confirm the effectiveness of this mask.</strong> With a high satisfaction rate, users report visible improvements in skin firmness, smoothness, and overall skin comfort. <strong>It has become a long-term favorite for women in their 30s, 40s, and beyond who are looking for real results.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggs0eGoHRpy_label","label":"ggs0eGoHRpy_label","default":"<p>SHOP NOW</p>"}],
